```{r pancreas 32273276, include=FALSE}

PMID_32273276 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32273276', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32273276 <- paste0(PMID_32273276$journal,' ', PMID_32273276$year, ' ', PMID_32273276$month,';', PMID_32273276$volume,'(', PMID_32273276$number,'):', PMID_32273276$pages)

PubMed_32273276 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32273276$eprint)

doi_32273276 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32273276$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
